# Marker directives for the DbMigrator service.
#
# Anchor inside the SeedDataAsync(...) method body — the admin-password
# fail-fast block must run BEFORE the actual seeding kicks off so the
# process aborts early when App:AdminPassword is unset or matches a
# known-leaked plaintext.
ANCHOR ^[[:space:]]*private[[:space:]]+async[[:space:]]+Task[[:space:]]+SeedDataAsync[(][)][[:space:]]*$
BLOCK admin-password-fail-fast
